373
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,040
<i>Tak tady.

374
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:21,960
<i>Ano.

375
00:18:24,710 --> 00:18:25,759
Pojď. Sedni si.

376
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:26,560
Dobře.

377
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:31,680
<i>A tady.

378
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:35,230
<i>Ještě tady.

379
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:36,200
<i>Dobře.

380
00:18:38,950 --> 00:18:39,750
Co je?

381
00:18:43,310 --> 00:18:44,110
Tu, tu, tu.

382
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:45,680
Já... já... se ...

383
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:47,150
Nech to na mně.

384
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:54,360
Nehýbej se.

385
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:01,800
Lechtáš.

386
00:19:15,950 --> 00:19:16,750
To je hrom.

387
00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:18,400
Ne. Neboj se.

388
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:20,980
<i>Žádný strach. Jsem u tebe.

