424
00:21:05,070 --> 00:21:06,790
<i>S největší pravděpodobnosti

425
00:21:06,950 --> 00:21:08,830
<i>máme otravu houbami.

426
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:12,110
<i>Jianbai.

427
00:21:15,950 --> 00:21:16,750
Gaoyangu.

428
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:17,720
Už jsi skončil?

429
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:21,590
Pospěš si. Už to nevydržím!

430
00:21:22,190 --> 00:21:23,040
<i>Vylez!

431
00:21:30,950 --> 00:21:31,750
Gaoyangu.

432
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:33,470
Gaoyangu, jak je ti?

433
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,310
<i>Co je s tebou?

434
00:21:41,470 --> 00:21:42,350
Gaoyangu.

